      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "う～……{user}さ～ん……\n芽衣はもうダメかもしれない……",
      "startTime": 99.64,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "何があったんだ、芽衣？",
      "startTime": 103.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんがお父さんに認めてもらうなら\nまずは二人で話さなきゃーって思ったの",
      "startTime": 108.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、どうやってそこまで持っていったらいいか\n分かんなくて……",
      "startTime": 115.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "『お父さんとお母さんがどれだけ大事な存在か』って\n怜ちゃんに沢山話したら、困った顔されちゃった",
      "startTime": 121.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃまあ……いきなり熱弁されたら驚くだろうな",
      "startTime": 126.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、ほんとどうしたらいいんだろう……？\n頭がパンクしそうだよ～……",
      "startTime": 137.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "こういう時は気分転換をした方がいいぞ\n少し散歩でもしないか？",
      "startTime": 145.21,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_01-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "は～い",
      "startTime": 147.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
